list_definition_mean.definition: of, natural to, concerning, or belonging to, mankind
ex_of_definition_list: human nature
The dog was so clever that he seemed almost human.

list_definition_mean.definition: a person
ex_of_definition_list: Humans are not as different from animals as we might think.

list_definition_mean.definition: something which a person does usually or regularly
ex_of_definition_list: He has the habit of going for a walk after dinner
She has an irritating habit of interrupting people.

list_definition_mean.definition: a tendency to do the same things that one has always done
ex_of_definition_list: I did it out of habit.

list_definition_mean.definition: a long loose piece of clothing worn by monks or nuns
ex_of_definition_list: a monk’s habit.

list_definition_mean.definition: a type of powerful explosive
ex_of_definition_list: a stick of dynamite.

list_definition_mean.definition: a person who looks after sick or injured people in hospital
ex_of_definition_list: She’s a qualified nurse.

list_definition_mean.definition: a person, usually a woman, who looks after small children
ex_of_definition_list: The children have gone out with their nurse.

list_definition_mean.definition: to look after sick or injured people, especially in a hospital
ex_of_definition_list: He was nursed back to health.

list_definition_mean.definition: to hold with care
ex_of_definition_list: She was nursing a kitten.

list_definition_mean.definition: to have or encourage (feelings eg of anger or hope) in oneself
ex_of_definition_list: She nursed a faint hope that he would mend his ways.

list_definition_mean.definition: a piece of ground on which flowers, vegetables etc are grown
ex_of_definition_list: a small garden at the front of the house
(also adjective) a garden slug.

list_definition_mean.definition: to work in a garden, usually as a hobby
ex_of_definition_list: The old lady does not garden much.

list_definition_mean.definition: a member of a race of wandering people
ex_of_definition_list: (also adjective) a gypsy caravan.

list_definition_mean.definition: difficult to understand or explain, or full of mystery

list_definition_mean.definition: a person who prepares people or animals for sport, a race etc
ex_of_definition_list: a personal trainer.

list_definition_mean.definition: happy and (as if) celebrating
ex_of_definition_list: a festive atmosphere.

list_definition_mean.definition: the spirit; the non-physical part of a person, which is often thought to continue in existence after he or she dies
ex_of_definition_list: People often discuss whether animals and plants have souls.

list_definition_mean.definition: a person
ex_of_definition_list: She’s a wonderful old soul.

list_definition_mean.definition: (of an enterprise etc) the organizer or leader
ex_of_definition_list: He is the soul of the whole movement.

list_definition_mean.definition: soul music
ex_of_definition_list: Her music mixes elements of soul and jazz.

list_definition_mean.definition: a ship or large lorry for carrying oil
ex_of_definition_list: an oil tanker.

list_definition_mean.definition: a load of goods sent by sea
ex_of_definition_list: a shipment of wine from Portugal.

list_definition_mean.definition: stone(work)

list_definition_mean.definition: an intense fear or hatred of something
ex_of_definition_list: She has a phobia about spiders.

list_definition_mean.definition: the act of converting
ex_of_definition_list: his conversion to Christianity
the conversion of the house into a hotel.

list_definition_mean.definition: a plant, grown in well-watered ground in tropical countries, whose seeds are used as food
ex_of_definition_list: fried rice.

list_definition_mean.definition: someone who does not eat any animal products such as meat, milk, cheese, or eggs
ex_of_definition_list: (also adjective) a vegan diet.

list_definition_mean.definition: (something which causes) great sorrow

list_definition_mean.definition: additional people who provide help when it is needed
ex_of_definition_list: The police officer requested some backup when the shooting began.

list_definition_mean.definition: a copy of a computer file that can be used in case the original is destroyed
ex_of_definition_list: You should always make a backup of the file you are working on.

ex_of_definition_list: We have a generator which we use as a backup if the power fails
(also adjective) a backup plan.

list_definition_mean.definition: (the act of) thinking about something, especially the needs or feelings of other people

list_definition_mean.definition: a fact to be taken into account in making a decision etc
ex_of_definition_list: The cost of the accommodation is our main consideration.

list_definition_mean.definition: a taxi
ex_of_definition_list: Could you call a cab for me?

list_definition_mean.definition: the driver’s compartment of a railway/railroad engine, lorry/truck etc

list_definition_mean.definition: a piece of paper etc giving one the right to something, eg a gift or discount price
ex_of_definition_list: This coupon gives 50 cents off your next purchase.

list_definition_mean.definition: a strong alcoholic drink made in Mexico
ex_of_definition_list: a bottle of tequila.

list_definition_mean.definition: a glass of tequila

ex_of_definition_list: a pedestrian walkway.

list_definition_mean.definition: to think (a person etc) guilty
ex_of_definition_list: Whom do you suspect (of the crime)?
I suspect him of killing the girl.

list_definition_mean.definition: to distrust
ex_of_definition_list: I suspected her motives / air of honesty.

list_definition_mean.definition: to think probable
ex_of_definition_list: I suspect that she’s trying to hide her true feelings
I began to suspect a plot.

list_definition_mean.definition: a person who is thought guilty
ex_of_definition_list: There are three possible suspects in this murder case.

list_definition_mean.definition: not trustworthy
ex_of_definition_list: I think his statement is suspect.

list_definition_mean.definition: to give advice to; to recommend
ex_of_definition_list: My lawyer advised me not to speak to any journalists.

list_definition_mean.definition: (with of) to inform
ex_of_definition_list: This letter is to advise you of our interest in your proposal.

list_definition_mean.definition: a place at which things (eg railway/railroad lines) join
ex_of_definition_list: a railway/railroad junction
There was an accident at the junction of Park Road and School Lane.

list_definition_mean.definition: the flesh of sheep, used as food
ex_of_definition_list: a leg of mutton.

list_definition_mean.definition: (often with about) to have or form ideas in one’s mind
ex_of_definition_list: Can babies think?
I was thinking about my mother.

list_definition_mean.definition: to have or form opinions in one’s mind; to believe
ex_of_definition_list: He thinks (that) the world is flat
What do you think of his poem?
What do you think about his suggestion?
He thought me very stupid.

list_definition_mean.definition: to intend or plan (to do something), usually without making a final decision
ex_of_definition_list: I must think what to do
I was thinking of/about going to London next week.

list_definition_mean.definition: to imagine or expect
ex_of_definition_list: I never thought to see you again
Little did he think that I would be there as well.

list_definition_mean.definition: the act of thinking
ex_of_definition_list: Go and have a think about it.

list_definition_mean.definition: to sell (goods) (usually in small quantities) to the person who is going to use them (rather than to someone who is going to sell them to someone else)
ex_of_definition_list: That particular guitar retails at £750.

list_definition_mean.definition: relating to the sale of goods in this way
ex_of_definition_list: a retail price.

list_definition_mean.definition: the activity of selling goods to customers for their own use
ex_of_definition_list: She works in retail.

list_definition_mean.definition: time which one can spend as one likes, especially when one does not have to work
ex_of_definition_list: She leads a life of leisure.
(also adjective) Ursula enjoys reading and gardening in her leisure time.

list_definition_mean.definition: the red fluid pumped through the body by the heart
ex_of_definition_list: Blood poured from the wound in his side.

list_definition_mean.definition: angry
ex_of_definition_list: I get very cross when I lose something.

list_definition_mean.definition: a symbol formed by two lines placed across each other, eg + or x
ex_of_definition_list: The cross on the map indicates where the treasure was buried.

list_definition_mean.definition: a lasting cause of suffering etc
ex_of_definition_list: Your rheumatism is a cross you will have to bear.

list_definition_mean.definition: the result of breeding two varieties of animal or plant
ex_of_definition_list: This dog is a cross between an alsatian and a labrador.

list_definition_mean.definition: any of several types of medal given for bravery etc
ex_of_definition_list: the Victoria Cross.

list_definition_mean.definition: to go from one side to the other
ex_of_definition_list: Let’s cross (the street)

list_definition_mean.definition: (opposite uncross) to place (two things) across each other
ex_of_definition_list: He sat down and crossed his legs.

list_definition_mean.definition: to go or be placed across (each other)
ex_of_definition_list: The roads cross in the centre/center of town.

list_definition_mean.definition: to meet and pass
ex_of_definition_list: Our letters must have crossed in the post.

list_definition_mean.definition: to put a line across
ex_of_definition_list: Cross your ‘t’s’.

list_definition_mean.definition: to breed (something) from two different varieties
ex_of_definition_list: I’ve crossed two varieties of rose.

list_definition_mean.definition: to go against the wishes of
ex_of_definition_list: If you cross me, you’ll regret it!

list_definition_mean.definition: going or placed across
ex_of_definition_list: cross-winds
cross-pieces.

list_definition_mean.definition: of mixed variety
ex_of_definition_list: a cross-breed.

list_definition_mean.definition: a young bird, especially a young hen
ex_of_definition_list: She keeps chickens.

list_definition_mean.definition: its flesh used as food
ex_of_definition_list: a plate of fried chicken.

list_definition_mean.definition: a coward
ex_of_definition_list: Don’t be such a chicken!

list_definition_mean.definition: able to be trusted or depended on
ex_of_definition_list: his trusty sword
a trusty friend.

list_definition_mean.definition: a maker’s name or trademark
ex_of_definition_list: a new brand of dog food
(also adjective) a brand name.

list_definition_mean.definition: a variety
ex_of_definition_list: He has his own brand of humour/humor.

list_definition_mean.definition: to mark cattle etc with a hot iron
ex_of_definition_list: The cows are branded for identification purposes.

list_definition_mean.definition: to make a permanent impression on
ex_of_definition_list: His name is branded on my memory.

list_definition_mean.definition: to attach (permanent) disgrace to
ex_of_definition_list: She was branded for life as a thief.

list_definition_mean.definition: strange; odd
ex_of_definition_list: a curious habit.

list_definition_mean.definition: anxious or interested (to learn)
ex_of_definition_list: I’m curious (to find out) whether he passed his exams.

list_definition_mean.definition: to keep from changing, being damaged or lost
ex_of_definition_list: We must conserve the country’s natural resources
This old building should be conserved.

list_definition_mean.definition: something preserved, eg fruits in sugar, jam etc
ex_of_definition_list: a jar of black cherry conserve.

list_definition_mean.definition: a repeated decoration or design on material etc
ex_of_definition_list: The dress is nice, but I don’t like the pattern.

list_definition_mean.definition: a model or guide for making something
ex_of_definition_list: a dress pattern.

list_definition_mean.definition: an example suitable to be copied
ex_of_definition_list: the pattern of good behaviour/behavior.

ex_of_definition_list: That apartment building has a beautiful penthouse
(also adjective) a penthouse flat.

list_definition_mean.definition: a sauce made from fruit, vegetables and spices
ex_of_definition_list: tomato chutney

list_definition_mean.definition: the sharing out of money or prizes won by chance, through drawing lots
ex_of_definition_list: Have you ever won anything on the lottery?

list_definition_mean.definition: a tube, usually made of metal, earthenware etc, through which water, gas etc can flow
ex_of_definition_list: a water pipe

list_definition_mean.definition: a small tube with a bowl at one end, in which tobacco is smoked
ex_of_definition_list: He smokes a pipe
(also adjective) pipe tobacco.

list_definition_mean.definition: a musical instrument consisting of a hollow wooden, metal etc tube through which the player blows or causes air to be blown in order to make a sound

list_definition_mean.definition: to convey gas, water etc by a pipe
ex_of_definition_list: Water is piped to the town from the reservoir.

list_definition_mean.definition: to play (music) on a pipe or pipes
ex_of_definition_list: He piped a tune.

list_definition_mean.definition: to speak in a high voice, make a high-pitched sound

list_definition_mean.definition: towards or in a low or lower position, level or state
ex_of_definition_list: He climbed down to the bottom of the ladder.

list_definition_mean.definition: on or to the ground
ex_of_definition_list: The little boy fell down and cut his knee.

list_definition_mean.definition: from earlier to later times
ex_of_definition_list: The recipe has been handed down in our family for years.

list_definition_mean.definition: from a greater to a smaller size, amount etc
ex_of_definition_list: Prices have been going down steadily.

list_definition_mean.definition: in a lower position on

list_definition_mean.definition: to a lower position on, by, through or along

list_definition_mean.definition: along

list_definition_mean.definition: to finish (a drink) very quickly, especially in one gulp

list_definition_mean.definition: small, soft feathers

list_definition_mean.definition: (of eg a cushion, ball etc) that can be filled with air for use
ex_of_definition_list: an inflatable beach ball.

list_definition_mean.definition: the bright light of something burning

list_definition_mean.definition: to burn with flames

list_definition_mean.definition: to become very hot, red etc

list_definition_mean.definition: made of, or having a pattern of, flowers
ex_of_definition_list: floral decorations
